### GraphQL PoC — IntelliJ HTTP Client
@host = http://localhost:8081

### 0. GraphiQL UI (브라우저 직접 접속)
# http://localhost:8081/graphiql

### 1. alcohol(id:1) — 단건 조회 (HTTP)
POST {{host}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ alcohol(id:1) { alcoholId korName engName cask abv volume } }"}


### 2. alcohols(ids:[1,5,10]) — 배치 조회 (HTTP)
POST {{host}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ alcohols(ids:[1,5,10]) { alcoholId korName cask abv } }"}


### 3. variables 사용 — query 와 변수 분리
POST {{host}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query Get($id: ID!) { alcohol(id: $id) { alcoholId korName engName imageUrl korCategory cask abv volume } }",
  "variables": { "id": 1 },
  "operationName": "Get"
}


### 4. 일부 필드만 — selection set 만 줄이기
POST {{host}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ alcohol(id:1) { korName } }"}


### 5. 잘못된 필드 — schema 검증 (자동 reject)
POST {{host}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ alcohol(id:1) { nonExistentField } }"}


### 6. SDL 직접 노출 (개발용 — schema printer)
GET {{host}}/graphql/schema


### 7. in-process 호출 — 같은 JVM 안에서 ExecutionGraphQlService 로 호출
GET {{host}}/api/graphql-poc/alcohol/1


### 8. 비교 — 일반 REST 알코올 상세 (hydrate 풍부 응답, region+tags 포함)
GET {{host}}/api/alcohols/1/detail
